  # Position:
  #
  # 0  Top
  # 1  Bottom
  # 2  Hide

  # Element type:
  #
  # t  Tags
  # s  Statustext (will take available space)
  # y  Systray (can be set only ONE time among all element)
  # l  Launcher (will be expended at launcher use)

